<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Image Search Abstraction Layer</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class='container'>
    <h1>Image Search Abstraction Layer</h1>
    <h3>User stories:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>I can get the image URLs, alt text and page urls for a set of images relating to a given search string.</li>
      <li>I can paginate through the responses by adding a ?offset=2 parameter to the URL. (Note, offset must be smaller or equal to 10)</li>
      <li>I can get a list of the most recently submitted search strings.</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>Example usage:</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>
        Pass search string
        <code>https://imagesearch-api-service.herokuapp.com/api/imagesearch/lolcats%20funny?offset=10 </code>
      </li>
      <li>
        View recent search queries
        <code>https://imagesearch-api-service.herokuapp.com/api/recentsearch</code>
      </li>
    </ol>

  </div>
</body>
</html>